{"tid":2240374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［香港連尼日利亞都不如！］尼日利亞抗警暴示威後 總統宣佈解散有問題警方部門並展開調查","createTime":"2020-10-12T15:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T16:48:28.000Z","uid":239336,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b849b29efc0dfc6e14261ab53db8bfa0cf789f56","tid":2240374,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"尼日利亞連日爆發反警暴示威，反對警隊一個部門目涉嫌非法逮捕民眾、勒索、實施酷刑甚至謀殺，總統周日宣佈即時解散這個被指違反人權的警方部門，並就警暴行為展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n總統布哈里（Muhammadu Buhari）的辦公室周日宣佈即時解散警方的特種反搶劫部隊（Special Anti-Robbery Squad，SARS），警方表示會調查「針對侵害市民」的指控，「罪魁禍首將受到懲罰」，而調查將會有民間及人權組織參與。SARS的警員會被調往其他部門，往後會另有安排取而代之。<br />\n<br />\n尼日利亞過去一周爆發示威，民眾不滿特種反搶劫部隊成員涉嫌非法逮捕、勒索、酷刑甚至謀殺的行為。網絡最近流傳一條片段，可見當地一名男子被警員殺死，當局曾否認片段內容並拘捕拍片者，結果引起公憤。示威起初只針對SARS，隨後擴展至全警隊。<br />\n<br />\n本月4日副總統也譴責警暴，直言自己「見到年輕男女被補，部份個案甚至有人被警察殘害或殺死，我非常關注亦很憤怒」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201012/XZS7V32GVRAIXEYWMX6JCJNR3M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2OrTr2nDhYg_dMUEaZ-DkWx5VOyrQDKLoHXCm_0oYDUilg1lq86FttXAY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201012%2FXZS7V32GVRAIXEYWMX6JCJNR3M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2OrTr2nDhYg_dMUEaZ-DkWx5VOyrQDKLoHXCm_0oYDUilg1lq86FttXAY&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2VxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=5a03faf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201012%2FXZS7V32GVRAIXEYWMX6JCJNR3M%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2OrTr2nDhYg_dMUEaZ-DkWx5VOyrQDKLoHXCm_0oYDUilg1lq86FttXAY&h=ef3beb87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201012/XZS7V32GVRAIXEYWMX6JCJNR3M/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2OrTr2nDhYg_dMUEaZ-DkWx5VOyrQDKLoHXCm_0oYDUilg1lq86FttXAY</a>"},{"pid":"12bd4e010187011e9218ec16289e691dc2b272f7","tid":2240374,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd848c69d6011afe790f22fe957b5b51ba7d2f73","tid":2240374,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73d28ecd8ea3c1e55ea3542ce28c5191fd0eb38","tid":2240374,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5201738ee3760ed3f5abbe95f23b7d807fe829af","tid":2240374,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:30:38.000Z","msg":"又考第一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1228fc3c4055e7ee6b3cd6814e6b1255c4b322","tid":2240374,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"真黑警"},{"pid":"05fd8eb8c035675d697aa28d7dfef4d9953b4fbc","tid":2240374,"uid":269202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"尼日尼亞終於都有人民覺醒<br />\n<br />\n仲記得之前佢地d人權組織周圍draw attention,不計手段"},{"pid":"aee2602e4e2eaf7ccc9e7b001e4368b573d7b57f","tid":2240374,"uid":2